lead_paragraph: The problems that have bogged down Ohio State's offense put the Buckeyes in a bind again. J.T. Barrett and Ohio State did enough in the fourth quarter against Northwestern to avoid a second consecutive upset loss.

headline.print_headline: No. 6 Ohio State Holds On to Beat Northwestern 24-20
